[Front-end sends payload]
      ↓
process_natural_interview:
  ├→ clean_cache
  ├→ build state (phase, question_idx, follow_up_count, history, text, etc.)
  ├→ route → 

      └──► Greeting Phase
            ├─ phase == "greeting"
            ├─ Greeting node sends “Hi! I’m Chris… How are you today?”
            └─ (front-end reply) → phase moves to "intro"

      └──► Intro Phase
            ├─ phase == "intro"
            ├─ Intro node sends company context + “Ready to start?”
            └─ (front-end reply) → phase moves to "questions", question_idx = 0

      └──► Questions Phase (process_answer_node)
            │
            ├──► 1. Intent Classification
            │       ├─ Is EndInterview? ──▶ complete_interview_node 
            │       ├─ Is RepeatQuestion? ──▶ ask_question_node (same idx) 
            │       ├─ Is PreviousQuestion? ──▶ question_idx-- + ask_question_node 
            │       ├─ Is ClarifyQuestion? ──▶ clarify handler (re-explain Q) 
            │       ├─ Is OffTopic? ──▶ off-topic redirect + next question 
            │       ├─ Is Hesitation? ──▶ gentle prompt + re-ask current Q 
            │       ├─ Is SmallTalk? ──▶ polite redirect + re-ask current Q 
            │       └─ Else (Intent == Answer) ──▶ go to step 2
            │
            └──► 2. Default “Answer” path
                    ├─ STAR & pattern analysis (heuristics)
                    ├─ on-topic? (LLM classifier)
                    │     ├─ No → off-topic redirect + next Q
                    │     └─ Yes → should_ask_followup?
                    │               ├─ Yes → LLM follow-up on same Q
                    │               └─ No  → LLM transition + next Q (or complete)
                    └─ form response and update question_idx & follow_up_count
      ↓
[Back-end returns bot_response + updated state]
      ↓
[Front-end displays next prompt or wraps up if done]
